II. Research & Project approval (Part 1)
1. Title of the projecta and tag line: Africa_connection
This project is about an african content about music, video and podcast(audio and lecture). It's an audio video collection application 
specific to Africa and sharing African culture(Music, history and current affairs). 
In addition to audio-visual content, a reading section will be integrated to enable the sharing of written
content (which could be of interest to deaf-mutes and other reading enthusiasts).
The main aim of this application is to share African content and culture. It will also help people over the Africa continent to 
connect each other(like facebook, tweeter) and will allow peaple to be together depending on their preference

2. Team Members and role
Team members are Abdoulaye, iAbas and Wisdom.
This project will have two main aspect, the backend and frontent. So for each aspect deepending on the team member ability task will
be assign.
3. Technology
Python, HTML & CSS, javascript, Flask framework, SQLAlquemy.
